nodes.body: Unfortunately we're getting build messages from ProofWidgets replayed during the Mathlib build. Not sure of the fix yet, it may require a new version. :-(
I've solved that problem just by silencing ProofWidgets, but now we're having more problems because Mathlib CI is running the `widgetJsAllTarget` in ProofWidgets, which is really shouldn't be.

Pull request successfully merged into master.
